notes.ConstructedIv: The counter for AES-GCM is reduced modulo 2**32. This test vector was constructed to test for correct wrapping of the counter.
notes.ZeroLengthIv: AES-GCM does not allow an IV of length 0. Encrypting with such an IV leaks the authentication key. Hence using an IV of length 0 is insecure even if the key itself is only used for a single encryption.
